Class PrimitiveAssignability

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.wala.core.util.PrimitiveAssignability
public class PrimitiveAssignability extends Object
Offers checks like ClassHierarchy.isAssignable but for primitives.

This Class does not consider Boxing / Unboxing
